data.description:
This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in the growing city of Maricopa offers a comfortable and spacious living environment. With four bedrooms, this home offers plenty of space for a family or for accommodating guests. The main living areas are adorned with elegant shutters, adding both style and privacy.
One of the standout features of this home is the large open kitchen, perfect for entertaining. It includes modern appliances, ample counter space, and an oversized island. As you step into the backyard, you'll find a lovely travertine back patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. The backyard also features turf grass, providing a lush and green space without the need for constant maintenance. A wonderful place to call home!
